snippet.title: Dawntrail is FF14's LAST CHANCE To Avoid DISASTER
snippet.description:
Given the lukewarm and sometimes outright hostile reactions to FF14's Dawntrail expansion. People have inevitably making the comparisons between it, and the dumpster fire that was Shadowlands.

Today we examine the differences between these MMO Expansions and why we think Dawntrail is much more similar to a different expansion, and why this could be FF14's last chance to avoid DISASTER.
----------
